♪Only a long gaze remains♪

17
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:25,610
♪A drop of tear♪

18
00:01:25,610 --> 00:01:29,490
♪Falls, burning my heart♪

19
00:01:29,490 --> 00:01:33,340
♪We loved without regret♪

20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:36,580
=My Destined Consort=

21
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:39,660
=Episode 26=

22
00:01:40,830 --> 00:01:41,670
Let me go.

23
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,520
Let go.

24
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:45,080
I need to see Master Jingming.

25
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,440
- Move.
- Let go.

26
00:01:47,270 --> 00:01:48,160
Let me go.

27
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,380
I need to see Master Jingming.

28
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,880
Get in.

29
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,270
I need to see Master Jingming.

30
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:55,830
Let me see Master Jingming.

31
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:57,110
Let me out.

32
00:01:57,110 --> 00:01:58,520
You want to see Master Jingming?

33
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,600
Everyone in Dongzhou knows

34
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,600
you risked people's lives

35
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,830
just to claim credit.

36
00:02:02,350 --> 00:02:04,190
Now, the whole city
is petitioning Prefect

37
00:02:04,190 --> 00:02:05,270
for your execution.

38
00:02:06,250 --> 00:02:08,280
Master Jingming has been placed
under house arrest

39
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,430
for pleading on your behalf.

40
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,040
I didn't do it.

41
00:02:11,350 --> 00:02:12,400
Let me out.

42
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,570
I need to see Master Jingming.

43
00:02:13,620 --> 00:02:15,330
We're at a critical moment
in the epidemic.

44
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:16,470
If the medication is stopped

45
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,670
or the prescription is changed,

46
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:18,720
the patients' bodies

47
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,840
won't be able to take it.

48
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,890
Please relay a message to the Prefect.

49
00:02:21,950 --> 00:02:23,440
Let me treat the people first.

50
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,910
He can punish me afterward.

51
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:26,120
Your message won't help.

52
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:28,430
Besides, who in Dongzhou
would still dare

53
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,790
to take your medicine?

54
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,440
I must see Master Jingming.

55
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:34,280
Let me see Master Jingming.

56
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:51,030
Master Jingming.

57
00:02:53,350 --> 00:02:54,520
Your Grace, why are you here?

58
00:02:54,820 --> 00:02:56,280
I heard about Consort Jiangli.

59
00:02:57,950 --> 00:02:59,320
Though I don't know medicine,

60
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,450
I believe in Jiangli's medical skills.

61
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:02,840
She would never

62
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,950
make such a mistake.

63
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:06,440
I agree.

64
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,750
Someone must be plotting
behind the scenes.

65
00:03:11,670 --> 00:03:12,710
Young Master, Your Grace.

66
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,950
I've got news on the bandits

67
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,060
you had me investigate.

68
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,320
What bandits?

69
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,000
Jiangli discovered

70
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,950
that previously,

71
00:03:20,950 --> 00:03:22,120
Dongzhou's military funds

72
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,510
were funneled through Jinsheng Bank

73
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:24,600
to support the bandits.

74
00:03:29,820 --> 00:03:30,840
How is it?

75
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:35,840
Jiangli was right.

76
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:37,880
Those so-called bandits

77
00:03:39,070 --> 00:03:40,600
are Lu Jingxiu's private troops.

78
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:42,280
Private troops?

79
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,950
Could it be that Jiangli's investigation

80
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:46,840
through Wind Pavilion's connections

81
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:48,280
alerted Jingxiu,

82
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:50,470
which led to her imprisonment?

83
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:53,190
If Lu Jingxiu has a private army,

84
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:54,910
it must be sizable by now.

85
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:56,670
After all these years,

86
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,630
he couldn't have just stockpiled troops.

87
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,400
He's probably

88
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:02,350
built up significant power.

89
00:04:06,510 --> 00:04:07,400
Perhaps,

90
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,470
Jiangli's incident

91
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,790
may just be the beginning.

92
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:12,600
Jingxiu has been plotting for years.

93
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,350
This

94
00:04:14,350 --> 00:04:15,670
will not end peacefully.

95
00:04:16,470 --> 00:04:17,430
And behind it,

96
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,160
there may be an even greater crisis.

97
00:04:20,470 --> 00:04:22,640
My mansion is riddled with danger.

98
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:24,230
Even if Jiangli is released,

99
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,430
she'll be trapped here with me.

100
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:28,310
This involves too many people

101
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:29,990
and is too dangerous.

102
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,520
Your Grace,
you should return to Xizhou asap.

103
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,680
No.

104
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:36,200
I'm staying not just for Dongzhou.

105
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,520
If we don't deal with Lu Jingxiu,

106
00:04:38,670 --> 00:04:39,600
people like Wen Du

107
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,720
might keep stirring up trouble

108
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,520
in Xizhou.

109
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,870
Peace will never come between us.

110
00:04:49,470 --> 00:04:51,470
We still need to think carefully

111
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,340
if there's a perfect solution.

112
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:06,350
How can you still stand here?

113
00:05:06,690 --> 00:05:07,550
It's been two days.

114
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:09,300
Master Jingming
hasn't even left his room.

115
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,640
What else can he do?

116
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,740
Do you have a better plan?

117
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:14,550
I'll sneak in through the back window
and knock him out.

118
00:05:14,550 --> 00:05:15,990
You can get Consort Jiangli out.

119
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:17,080
Let's run.

120
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:19,920
Go ahead.

121
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:21,150
I'll collect your corpse.

122
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,460
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

123
00:05:40,790 --> 00:05:41,760
Don't worry, Jingming.

124
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,960
We were very careful.

125
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,400
No one saw us.

126
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,880
Jingming,

127
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:49,230
we heard about Jiangli.

128
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,040
What are you going to do?

129
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,230
Should we break her out of prison?

130
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:55,310
The priority now is to find out

131
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,800
the real cause of the patients' deaths

132
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,640
to clear Jiangli's name

133
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,160
and exonerate her

134
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:01,740
from killing people with medicine.

135
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,990
Actually, on the way back,

136
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:07,040
I tried to investigate the temple,

137
00:06:07,670 --> 00:06:08,790
but Jingxiu's Golden Guards

138
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:09,990
had it surrounded.

139
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:11,960
My soldiers couldn't get close.

140
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,880
Jingxing,

141
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,230
watch your words.

142
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:17,720
We're investigating a case,

143
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,770
not having a war.

144
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:21,280
Jingming is right.

145
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:23,280
You should be careful with your words.

146
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,670
I'm just worried for Jingming.

147
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,400
Rumors are flying around the city.

148
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,080
They say Jiangli

149
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:31,160
used the people's lives

150
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:33,550
to help Jingming become the Prefect.

151
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,470
The public outrage is boiling over.

152
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,680
Also,

153
00:06:36,910 --> 00:06:38,280
Jingxiu is fanning the flames.

154
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,760
He's putting on quite a show.

155
00:06:40,470 --> 00:06:41,980
Yesterday, he was comforting the sick.

156
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:44,080
Today, he's brought in monks
to chant for the dead.

157
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,400
He's always attracting attention.

158
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:46,760
Let him be.

159
00:06:47,470 --> 00:06:48,840
Right now, saving Jiangli

160
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:49,680
is more important.

161
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:52,040
So, what's our next move?

162
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:55,310
Young Master,

163
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,110
Princess Chuya's palanquin
stopped outside.

164
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,400
What is she doing here?

165
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,870
Jingming, it's not appropriate

166
00:07:02,870 --> 00:07:04,350
for outsiders to see us here.

167
00:07:04,350 --> 00:07:05,670
We'll take our leave.

168
00:07:06,470 --> 00:07:07,310
We'll go now.

169
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:21,150
Master Jingming.

170
00:07:22,230 --> 00:07:23,410
Your Grace, you came so late.

171
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:24,840
What is so urgent?

172
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,310
I've thought of a perfect solution.

173
00:07:29,110 --> 00:07:30,200
What perfect solution?

174
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,520
My medicine couldn't have gone wrong.

175
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,520
What exactly is going on?

176
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:54,900
(Prefect's Mansion)
Father,

177
00:07:54,900 --> 00:07:56,160
this is the list of the patients

178
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,960
and relief expenses I compiled.

179
00:07:58,470 --> 00:07:59,310
Please take a look.

180
00:08:05,550 --> 00:08:06,390
Not bad.

181
00:08:06,990 --> 00:08:07,910
Well done.

182
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:09,250
My Lord,

183
00:08:09,250 --> 00:08:10,700
Princess Chuya requests an audience.

184
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,470
What's she here for now?

185
00:08:12,470 --> 00:08:14,080
She might be here to say goodbye.

186
00:08:14,990 --> 00:08:15,830
Father,

187
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:18,160
with the plague spreading in Dongzhou,

188
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,400
maybe she's scared.

189
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,430
Bring the princess in.

190
00:08:33,190 --> 00:08:34,360
Greetings, My Lord.

191
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:37,160
Greetings, Master Jingxiu.

192
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,710
I've come today

193
00:08:40,710 --> 00:08:41,830
to ask the Prefect

194
00:08:41,950 --> 00:08:43,320
to grant a marriage

195
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,560
between me and Master Jingming.

196
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,640
You want to marry Jingming?

197
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:48,510
Your Grace,

198
00:08:49,090 --> 00:08:51,040
Jingming is currently a criminal.

199
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,910
Though it hasn't been clarified yet,

200
00:08:53,550 --> 00:08:55,960
the fact that Father hasn't punished him
is already a mercy.

201
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,590
At this time, granting a marriage

202
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,160
wouldn't be appropriate.

203
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,630
Whether it's mercy or punishment,
it has nothing to do with me.

204
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:03,910
All I know is

205
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:05,280
that the Grand Princess of Xizhou

206
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:08,000
is to marry Master Jingming of Dongzhou.

207
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,280
Dongzhou has many fine young men.

208
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:12,430
Why insist on Jingming?

209
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,120
Besides,

210
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,320
didn't he

211
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,880
reject you in public that day?

212
00:09:18,190 --> 00:09:19,670
He rejected me back then

213
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,310
because he had a consort.

214
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:22,910
But things are different now.

215
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,430
I believe

216
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:25,430
Dongzhou

217
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:27,710
needs someone like me to be his consort.

218
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,200
Your Grace,

219
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,360
with your background

220
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,830
and nobility in Xizhou,

221
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:35,280
you should marry someone
of equal status.

222
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,240
Only then can the alliance between us

223
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,430
be truly beneficial.

224
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,840
I'll even marry a criminal

225
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,160
if I like him.

226
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:43,950
I won't marry even a king

227
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:46,640
if I don't like him.

228
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,120
Among the four states,

229
00:09:48,430 --> 00:09:50,160
I don't think there's a man

230
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:51,910
who matches my status.

231
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,590
So, Master Jingxiu,

232
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:55,550
you'd better drop that thought.

233
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,600
My Lord,

234
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:02,280
I want to marry

235
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,880
the one I love.

236
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:06,400
If I can marry Master Jingming,

237
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:07,670
the two states

238
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:09,340
will surely
form a century-long alliance.

239
00:10:09,590 --> 00:10:10,550
Xizhou will also

240
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:12,070
start trading with Dongzhou

241
00:10:12,070 --> 00:10:13,360
and reduce tariffs.

242
00:10:13,550 --> 00:10:14,760
As for the pros and cons,

243
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,910
I don't think

244
00:10:16,090 --> 00:10:17,120
you need a junior like me

245
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,830
to spell them out for you.

246
00:10:19,710 --> 00:10:21,550
Summon Lady Shu and Master Jingming.

247
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:30,710
You're here.

248
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:34,520
The princess has requested
a marriage again.

249
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:35,790
She wants

250
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,280
to marry Jingming.

251
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:39,550
What?

252
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,480
Lady Shu,

253
00:10:43,070 --> 00:10:45,590
we in Xizhou are straightforward,

254
00:10:45,910 --> 00:10:47,550
so I'll speak plainly.

255
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,240
You are Master Jingming's mother.

256
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,120
If I marry him,

257
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,160
I'll treat you much better

258
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:56,950
than Shen Jiangli.

259
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:59,280
I can manage the household

260
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:01,550
and help with Master Jingming's work.

261
00:11:02,070 --> 00:11:02,910
But

262
00:11:03,070 --> 00:11:03,910
Jiangli...

263
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,000
Master Jingming,

264
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,710
will you marry me?

265
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:12,760
Jingming won't marry you.

266
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:15,550
I agree.

267
00:11:17,550 --> 00:11:18,520
I agree

268
00:11:19,070 --> 00:11:20,360
to marry the princess.

269
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:24,840
Jingming,

270
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:27,790
do you know the consequences?

271
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,670
Jiangli was just imprisoned,

272
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,310
and now you're rushing to marry another.

273
00:11:31,310 --> 00:11:32,830
What will the people think of you?

274
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:35,590
Even if she was at fault,

275
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:38,550
they'll say you're heartless.

276
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,400
The princess is devoted to me.

277
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,400
She's willing to offer herself

278
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,750
even before the cause of the deaths

279
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,550
is known.

280
00:11:47,430 --> 00:11:48,710
If I turn her down now,

281
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,360
wouldn't that be heartless too?

282
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,360
Jingming,

283
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:54,950
Jiangli...

284
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:56,040
Don't worry, Lady Shu.

285
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,280
I'll be Master Jingming's consort.

286
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:01,280
As for Shen Jiangli,

287
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:04,480
