My marriage with Master Jingming

577
00:25:46,870 --> 00:25:48,550
is of great importance to both states.

578
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:50,280
So, it must be done properly.

579
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:51,600
Lu Jingming,

580
00:25:52,590 --> 00:25:53,630
have you forgotten

581
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:55,790
that you promised me

582
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,000
you'd protect Jiangli for life?

583
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:04,040
Times have changed.

584
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:05,600
Moreover,

585
00:26:05,790 --> 00:26:07,000
this is my family matter.

586
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:09,590
There's no need to trouble you.

587
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,320
- You...
- Zimo.

588
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:12,390
Let's go.

589
00:26:18,130 --> 00:26:19,960
When do you plan to tell her

590
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,310
about your divorce?

591
00:26:27,350 --> 00:26:28,190
Divorce?

592
00:26:30,150 --> 00:26:31,720
Chuya is the Grand Princess of Xizhou.

593
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,200
She's of noble status.

594
00:26:35,070 --> 00:26:36,870
So, she should be the consort.

595
00:26:38,790 --> 00:26:39,830
You're still a suspect

596
00:26:39,830 --> 00:26:41,520
regarding the epidemic.

597
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,920
So, you can't be

598
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:46,040
the consort.

599
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:52,200
You should leave Dongzhou asap.

600
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:55,920
Divorce?

601
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:58,320
Yes.

602
00:26:59,390 --> 00:27:00,390
We indeed need a divorce.

603
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:05,280
After the epidemic is over,

604
00:27:06,700 --> 00:27:07,830
I will leave on my own

605
00:27:08,630 --> 00:27:09,960
without your reminder.

606
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:17,240
Jiangli.

607
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:22,630
You...

608
00:27:22,630 --> 00:27:23,630
Are you alright?

609
00:27:30,520 --> 00:27:31,360
Young Master.

610
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:32,980
The physician is here.

611
00:27:35,390 --> 00:27:36,230
Let her in.

612
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,540
Greetings, Master Jingming.

613
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,760
Greetings, Your Grace.

614
00:27:42,760 --> 00:27:44,030
Ms. Gao, no need for formalities.

615
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:46,390
You must've been exhausted
after your long journey.

616
00:27:46,870 --> 00:27:47,960
It's nothing.

617
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:49,350
Princess Chuya ordered this.

618
00:27:49,350 --> 00:27:50,690
I don't dare claim any exhaustion.

619
00:27:51,780 --> 00:27:54,750
Ms. Gao is the national physician
of Xizhou.

620
00:27:54,950 --> 00:27:57,070
She's renowned for her skills
in medicine and poison.

621
00:27:57,130 --> 00:27:59,390
She's taken care of me
since I was a child.

622
00:27:59,670 --> 00:28:00,960
She is someone I trust.

623
00:28:01,870 --> 00:28:02,970
Since she is one of our own,

624
00:28:03,180 --> 00:28:04,250
I will speak frankly.

625
00:28:05,150 --> 00:28:06,040
The reason

626
00:28:06,490 --> 00:28:08,520
we invited Ms. Gao from far away

627
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:11,070
is to investigate the sudden deaths

628
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:12,110
of the patients here.

629
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:14,870
Ms. Gao, please help us.

630
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:16,310
Of course, I will.

631
00:28:16,310 --> 00:28:17,550
Is there anything wrong?

632
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:19,750
May I inspect the prescriptions
and the pharmacy?

633
00:28:20,390 --> 00:28:21,230
Of course.

634
00:28:21,630 --> 00:28:22,470
Yunyi,

635
00:28:22,870 --> 00:28:24,070
take Ms. Gao to the site

636
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:24,920
to inspect it

637
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,110
and explain the situation

638
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:27,390
along the way.

639
00:28:28,080 --> 00:28:29,010
Ms. Gao,

640
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:29,930
this way, please.

641
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:30,830
I will take my leave.

642
00:28:34,520 --> 00:28:35,360
Don't worry.

643
00:28:35,870 --> 00:28:37,550
Be it fragrance or poison,

644
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:39,590
if Ms. Gao intervenes,

645
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:41,200
nothing will go undetected.

646
00:28:43,070 --> 00:28:43,910
Let's hope so.

647
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,630
Everyone, drink the medicine.

648
00:28:47,630 --> 00:28:48,550
Once you're better,

649
00:28:48,550 --> 00:28:50,310
you'll reunite with your families.

650
00:28:50,520 --> 00:28:52,390
Something's wrong with the medicine.

651
00:28:52,390 --> 00:28:53,440
We won't drink it.

652
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:54,550
Think carefully.

653
00:28:55,280 --> 00:28:56,590
When you were at your lowest,

654
00:28:56,720 --> 00:28:58,110
who stepped forward?

655
00:28:58,480 --> 00:29:00,520
Even when everyone doubted her,

656
00:29:00,520 --> 00:29:01,830
she never backed down.

657
00:29:02,040 --> 00:29:03,550
With your current condition,

658
00:29:03,550 --> 00:29:05,310
if you don't accept treatment now,

659
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,870
it will be too late.

660
00:29:07,550 --> 00:29:10,070
I hope you will give yourselves a chance

661
00:29:10,350 --> 00:29:11,590
and trust us once more.

662
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:13,720
Look.

663
00:29:15,350 --> 00:29:16,960
Look, she drank it.

664
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:22,830
You added licorice to the medicine,

665
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,590
which suppressed the bitterness.

666
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,410
You know medicine?

667
00:29:29,630 --> 00:29:30,790
Let's try it too.

668
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:38,910
Thanks.

669
00:29:50,310 --> 00:29:51,830
May I ask what your name is?

670
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:54,680
Ye Nanxing.

671
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:56,150
Goodbye.

672
00:29:58,130 --> 00:29:59,000
Jiangli,

673
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,280
after taking this medicine,

674
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:02,540
the residual heat in their bodies
will be alleviated.

675
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,680
Then we should return.

676
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,200
These are the herbs

677
00:30:10,210 --> 00:30:12,110
we collected from the site back then.

678
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:15,190
Sir,

679
00:30:15,390 --> 00:30:16,520
after the patients died,

680
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:18,070
did anyone else enter the area?

681
00:30:18,280 --> 00:30:19,870
No. Shortly after the incident,

682
00:30:19,870 --> 00:30:21,880
Master Jingming ordered us
to seal off this place.

683
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:22,960
No one has entered.

684
00:30:23,870 --> 00:30:26,200
Are these the medicinal residues
the patients consumed?

685
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:28,390
It's all here.

686
00:30:28,390 --> 00:30:29,750
Please begin the examination now.

687
00:30:42,150 --> 00:30:43,140
Have you found anything?

688
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,150
Please be patient.

689
00:30:46,910 --> 00:30:47,970
The bowl in your left hand

690
00:30:47,970 --> 00:30:49,580
was used by the deceased villager.

691
00:30:49,580 --> 00:30:50,630
The one in your right hand

692
00:30:50,630 --> 00:30:51,720
was used by Master Jingming

693
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:53,360
to test the medicine
for Consort Jiangli.

694
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:56,120
Is there a problem?

695
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:59,280
Sir, we need to return to the mansion

696
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:00,630
to check the details carefully.

697
00:31:00,760 --> 00:31:01,960
Let's leave now.

698
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:07,520
Master Jingming, look.

699
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,200
The white powder on the left

700
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,320
is scraped

701
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:11,590
from the deceased victim's bowl.

702
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:13,520
I've compared it with your bowl.

703
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:15,150
There's no such substance in your bowl.

704
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,590
What is this?

705
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,830
Please give me some alkaline water.

706
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:21,440
Yunyi.

707
00:31:21,870 --> 00:31:22,710
Yes.

708
00:31:23,340 --> 00:31:24,680
It's slightly sticky to the touch

709
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:25,750
and resembles salt grains.

710
00:31:25,750 --> 00:31:27,280
I think it's mirabilite.

711
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:28,120
Mirabilite?

712
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:30,720
Is it poisonous?

713
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:31,710
No.

714
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:33,070
I've seen the prescription before.

715
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:34,310
The victims of this plague

716
00:31:34,310 --> 00:31:36,550
generally had mild dysentery symptoms.

717
00:31:37,590 --> 00:31:38,790
If mirabilite was added,

718
00:31:38,790 --> 00:31:40,150
it would exacerbate the dysentery

719
00:31:40,150 --> 00:31:41,680
and cause rapid death

720
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,110
within a short period.

721
00:31:43,790 --> 00:31:45,040
But I had people

722
00:31:45,040 --> 00:31:46,350
inspect the herbs and residues

723
00:31:46,870 --> 00:31:48,200
and didn't find any medicine.

724
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:50,310
That's the brilliance of the murderer.

725
00:31:50,630 --> 00:31:52,310
Mirabilite is colorless and volatile,

726
00:31:52,630 --> 00:31:54,150
and it dissolves in water

727
00:31:54,150 --> 00:31:55,240
without high temperatures.

728
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:57,530
However, after a long time,

729
00:31:57,550 --> 00:31:58,760
it will still leave traces.

730
00:31:59,520 --> 00:32:00,630
It's truly malicious.

731
00:32:04,280 --> 00:32:05,250
Master Jingming, look.

732
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:07,240
My hand just touched the white powder.

733
00:32:07,830 --> 00:32:09,630
If I put my hand in the water now

734
00:32:09,630 --> 00:32:11,070
and the color changes,

735
00:32:11,070 --> 00:32:11,990
it will prove

736
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:12,960
that this is

737
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:13,830
definitely mirabilite.

738
00:32:20,720 --> 00:32:21,830
It changed.

739
00:32:22,150 --> 00:32:23,110
We must find out

740
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:24,480
who is behind this.

741
00:32:25,760 --> 00:32:26,720
And

742
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,760
what is this?

743
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:30,240
I found this in another bowl.

744
00:32:30,590 --> 00:32:31,430
However,

745
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:32,850
it doesn't seem like medicine,

746
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,020
so I brought it back

747
00:32:34,020 --> 00:32:35,300
for Master Jingming to inspect.

748
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,280
This is...

749
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,320
Horse feed?

750
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:50,380
This is indeed horse feed,

751
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:52,310
but it's not the feed from our mansion.

752
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:53,960
This inferior horse feed

753
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:56,240
is used for horses that transport goods.

754
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,040
Ms. Gao,

755
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,720
to avoid alerting the enemy,

756
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,310
you must stay here

757
00:33:01,310 --> 00:33:02,290
for now.

758
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:04,070
When the right moment comes,

759
00:33:04,200 --> 00:33:05,150
I will have someone

760
00:33:05,150 --> 00:33:06,790
send you to the mission.

761
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:10,040
Thank you, Master Jingming.

762
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:12,830
Yunyi.

763
00:33:12,830 --> 00:33:13,680
Young Master.

764
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,550
I will give you the results
within three days.

765
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:16,800
Go ahead.

766
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:21,920
Are you thinking

767
00:33:22,110 --> 00:33:24,040
Lu Jingxiu is behind this again?

768
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:27,280
Until the truth is uncovered,

769
00:33:28,870 --> 00:33:30,280
we must not leak any information.

770
00:33:31,300 --> 00:33:37,460
(Master Jingming's Mansion)

771
00:34:02,100 --> 00:34:06,190
♪May you be free from a long journey♪

772
00:34:06,700 --> 00:34:12,470
♪May you return
without suffering from the storm♪

773
00:34:14,180 --> 00:34:19,330
♪I quietly search in my heart♪

774
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:22,980
(Divorce Letter)

775
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:27,000
I will ask you one last time.

776
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:30,320
If you have any reasons,

777
00:34:31,870 --> 00:34:32,920
tell me.

778
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,310
I won't hold it against you.

779
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:37,950
No.

780
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:40,630
You truly want to marry Chuya

781
00:34:42,110 --> 00:34:43,290
and truly wish to divorce me?

782
00:34:45,070 --> 00:34:45,910
Yes.

783
00:34:48,040 --> 00:34:49,710
These are your true words?

784
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,590
There isn't a single lie?

785
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:54,910
Yes.

786
00:34:58,710 --> 00:34:59,550
Good.

787
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:02,630
Remember what you said today.

788
00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:06,550
I will take Yanyan and leave.

789
00:35:07,750 --> 00:35:08,750
From now on,

790
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,840
Yanyan and I

791
00:35:11,860 --> 00:35:13,710
will be away from you.

792
00:35:14,690 --> 00:35:15,750
We'll never meet again.

793
00:35:16,750 --> 00:35:17,880
Master Jingming,

794
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:20,270
I hope you can soar

795
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,190
and possess immense power.

796
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:25,550
I'll sign

797
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:27,380
the divorce letter.

798
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:30,860
(Divorce Letter)

799
00:35:32,910 --> 00:35:38,130
♪One only makes one promise
in this one life♪

800
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:43,950
♪However fast time goes by,
you still wouldn't know my feelings♪

801
00:35:44,130 --> 00:35:47,180
♪I can't hold on;
your face is like water♪

802
00:35:47,180 --> 00:35:51,660
♪Only your words remain♪

803
00:35:51,660 --> 00:35:55,990
♪Watching the moonlight
gradually disappear on the horizon♪

804
00:35:56,960 --> 00:36:02,060
♪There's only an incense stick of time
between us♪

805
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:09,600
♪Will you remember me
after burning away thousands of flowers♪

806
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,400
Jiangli,

807
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:26,550
will you really divorce Master Jingming?

808
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,520
What do you plan to do next?

809
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:30,190
From now on,

810
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,920
I'm no longer your sister-in-law.

811
00:36:32,270 --> 00:36:33,920
The plague has been stabilized.

812
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:35,480
I don't want to know

813
00:36:35,640 --> 00:36:36,960
about the conspiracies involved.

814
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:38,630
I only want to take Yanyan

815
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:40,040
and leave this place of strife.

816
00:36:40,520 --> 00:36:42,550
But Yanyan is now with Lady Shu.

817
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:45,750
I don't know if she
will allow him to leave.

818
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,630
That's why I've come to find you.

819
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:49,950
Now,

820
00:36:50,270 --> 00:36:52,040
Yanyan's identity
is different from before.

821
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:54,000
He's the Prefect's eldest grandson.

822
00:36:54,270 --> 00:36:55,360
Lady Shu

823
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:57,630
won't let me take Yanyan away easily.

824
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,400
So, Jiangli,

825
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:03,110
how should I cooperate with you

826
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:04,440
to get Yanyan out?

827
00:37:05,590 --> 00:37:06,590
Right now,

828
00:37:07,070 --> 00:37:08,670
I can't enter the Prefect's Mansion

829
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:10,190
because I've been falsely accused.

830
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:12,520
But you can help me.

831
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,470
You can go and greet them there.

832
00:37:14,470 --> 00:37:15,750
I'll disguise myself as your maid

833
00:37:15,750 --> 00:37:16,590
and go in with you.

834
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,280
Zimo,

835
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:21,750
please wait for me outside.

836
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:24,550
The Prefect's Mansion

837
00:37:24,750 --> 00:37:25,690
is heavily guarded now.

838
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:27,520
Even if you get in,

839
00:37:28,450 --> 00:37:29,520
it will be

840
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,440
incredibly difficult

841
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:32,670
to sneak Yanyan out unnoticed.

842
00:37:33,590 --> 00:37:35,190
But I have to take the risk.

843
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:36,590
I have no other way.

844
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:38,040
However hard it is, I must try.

845
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:41,190
We can first approach Lady Shu.

846
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:42,440
She is also a mother.

847
00:37:42,570 --> 00:37:43,840
If she is willing to help you,

848
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:45,740
getting Yanyan out will be much easier.

849
00:37:48,450 --> 00:37:49,710
But you must promise me

850
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,480
not to act recklessly.

851
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,000
Even if she refuses today,

852
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:54,420
we can always try again

853
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,970
as long as we don't alert the Prefect.

854
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,320
So,

855
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,400
you must follow my lead

856
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:59,320
in every action.

857
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,960
If you can do this,

858
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:02,680
I will take you
into the Prefect's Mansion.

859
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:04,320
Don't worry.

860
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,040
I will not act impulsively.

861
00:38:26,403 --> 00:38:30,163
♪The sound of the flute lingers,
making the night more tender♪

862
